              {
                "text": "The “Fasal Pradarshan” scheme under the Agriculture Department of the Rajasthan Government allocates grants to organize field and crop demonstrations on farmers' fields. These demonstrations aim to disseminate advanced crop production methods and the latest agricultural technology, educating farmers about innovative techniques such as precision farming and crop management practices to enhance their understanding and adoption of modern agricultural practices."
